ClassDef.Name: Physical

Properties.Name: Anchored
Properties.Description: Determines whether this object is affected by physics.

Properties.Name: CanCollide
Properties.Description: Determines whether this object can collide with other objects.

Properties.Name: Velocity
Properties.Description: Determines the linear velocity of this object.

Properties.Name: AngularVelocity
Properties.Description: Determines the angular velocity of this object.

Methods.Name: SetNetworkAuthority
Methods.Description: Sets the network authority of this object to the specified player.

Events.Name: Touched
Events.Description: Fires when this object has collide with other object

Events.Name: TouchEnded
Events.Description: Fires when this object has stopped colliding with other object

Events.Name: MouseEnter
Events.Description: Fires when cursor is hovered on this object. Only fired locally

Events.Name: MouseExit
Events.Description: Fires when cursor leaves this object. Only fired locally

Events.Name: Clicked
Events.Description: Fires when this object has been clicked by a player

ClassDef.Description: Physical represents an object affected by physics in the world.
